os Home Entertainment || ''Psycho'': Pop Art || DVD, Blu-ray || July 12, 2016\n|-\n| Shout! Factory || ''Psycho IV: The Beginning'' || Blu-ray || August 23, 2016\n|-\n| Shout! Factory || ''Psycho'' (1998) || Blu-ray || May 9, 2017\n|-\n| Universal Studios Home Entertainment || ''Psycho'': Complete 4-Movie Collection || DVD || September 12, 2017\n|-\n| Universal Studios Home Entertainment || ''Psycho'': Complete 4-Movie Collection || Blu-ray || November 14, 2017\n|-\n| Universal Studios Home Entertainment || ''Psycho II'', ''Psycho III'', ''Psycho IV: The Beginning'' || Blu-ray || August 28, 2018\n|}\n\n==Reception==\n\n===Box office performance===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Film\n! rowspan=\"2\" | U.S. release date\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Budget \n! colspan=\"3\" | Box office revenue \n|-\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"| United States\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"| International\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"| Worldwide \n|-\n| ''[[Psycho (1960 film)|Psycho]]''\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | June 16, 1960\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $806,947<ref name=\"Mojo\">{{cite web |title=Psycho (1960) |url=https://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=psycho.htm|website=[[Box Office Mojo]] |accessdate=October 20, 2014}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $32,000,000<ref name=\"Mojo\">{{cite web |title=Psycho (1960) |url=https://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=psycho.htm|website=[[Box Office Mojo]] |accessdate=October 20, 2014}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| TBA\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| TBA\n|-\n| ''[[Psycho II (film)|Psycho II]]''\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | June 3, 1983\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $5,000,000<ref name=\"pshchomovies\">{{Cite web | url = http://www.thepsychomovies.com/films/psycho2/ | title = Psycho II | website = The Psycho Movies | accessdate = June 30, 2013 | url-status = dead | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130603054014/http://www.thepsychomovies.com/films/psycho2/ | archivedate = June 3, 2013 }}